{"tw": {"3759330": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "煉金術士的秘藥", "steam_appid": 3759330, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3759330/extras/f1ba88cbbc4ea5098a2f1052f767e0b9.avif?t=1765940625\" width=348 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     將扮演身為煉金術士的諾亞，與安妮攜手展開刺激冒險！<br>     除了緊張戰鬥和精彩主線劇情外，夜晚上每個決定都能使諾亞與安妮展發不同的劇情！<br>     來體驗這場充滿激情與冒險的史詩旅程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3759330/extras/6ae99261fb52313aac996fc4cac96273.avif?t=1765940625\" width=237 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     歐姆大陸上發生了「哥布林的進擊」事件發生後，<br>     各處依然持續受到哥布林的侵害，但沒人知道他們的目的。<br>     某一天，安妮因緣巧合下拯救了諾亞，命運之輪亦隨即轉動。<br>     他們合力一起對抗哥布林，並一步一步掀開哥布林們的陰謀！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3759330/extras/6c9095f7827c6ffacab56da8b86ea5a3.avif?t=1765940625\" width=466 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     刺激緊張的回合制玩法，運用安妮的魔法與諾亞的煉金來攜手對抗哥布林！<br>     透過訓練來增強能力，同時需要種植和煉金來獲取道具來協助戰鬥！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3759330/extras/ce7c9f32342e19b54be219c7068a8d5f.avif?t=1765940625\" width=513 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     通過不斷的探索來觸發事件，可能會是遇到寶箱，商人，哥布林，同伴等等的事件。<br>     甚至亦可能觸發特殊的未知事件？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea